{"tid":1592932,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE成員透視又爆乳　子瑜露肩曬腿被封「台灣女神」","createTime":"2019-09-24T23:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T13:44:55.000Z","uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"465d1aa3e85f20a364ee2abb9fbba75bbcdae657","tid":1592932,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:55:51.000Z","msg":"collage<br />\n▲MOMO在新歌造型上十分性感；子瑜被封「台灣女神」。（圖／TWICE YouTube、翻攝tvreport）<br />\nA Decrease font size. A Increase font size.<br />\n<br />\n南韓夯團TWICE今（23日）發行第八張迷你專輯《Feel Special》回歸樂壇並舉辦紀念SHOWCASE活動，「JYP娛樂」就表示，有焦慮症的Mina雖然有參與MV製作，但不會參加這次的打歌活動，而隊長志效在準備的過程中不慎扭傷，之後將會以坐在椅子上的方式表演。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲Mina雖有參與MV拍攝（上圖），但不參與打歌；志效不慎扭傷，日後將坐在椅子上表演（下圖右）。（圖／TWICE YouTube、VLIVE）"},{"pid":"d8f792875b2c814077c9295ccdfac717855da248","tid":1592932,"uid":47605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"a1925a1187f8eabf3b8544190bbf4a0abb559073","tid":1592932,"uid":71632,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1569238798-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a-1392x1083.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F1569238798-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a-1392x1083.jpg&h=adac864a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f1cf04da72cc35847a4ad3243f6c8e2ed664ab6","tid":1592932,"uid":171598,"like":25,"dislike":16,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:57:17.000Z","msg":"好撚柒呀 點解會有人like佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /